title: Undeniably Delightful! Home in Bonney Lake. 3 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: Welcome to this Recently Updated 2 Story Home!

Luxury Vinyl Flooring in the Kitchen*  Freshly Painted Interior* Main Floor consists of a Great Room Concept w/Gas Fireplace and Lg Kitchen that has an  Island w/with Breakfast Bar, SS Appliances, Granite Counters & Walk-In Pantry & Laundry Area* Upstairs is the Lg  Primary Suite w/Lg WIC and 5 piece Ensuite w/a Lg Soaking Tub & Walk-In Shower* You will also find Two other  Nice Sized Bedrooms & Main Full Bath, there is even an area in the hall that could be set up a Computer Desk or Study  area*
In the Backyard you'll find a Lovely Gazebo (Great Place for a Hot Tub) just outside the French Doors to the Patio,  Fully Fenced and enough room for whatever you can imagine.
